Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:05.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:06.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:10.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you want to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:16.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,To that place where I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:18.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:21.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What did I just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow, you just fell asleep for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:37.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looks like you should get to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Lack of sleep isn't good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:46.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'll become oversensitive and think things you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:49.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good night, Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I still love Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:01:00.85,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(268,286)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}With You Again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:59.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I can, I want to be with Linda forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:04.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:07.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stop my heart from dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:14.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Crying and laughing, we never forget our memories together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:24.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Finding your true self
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:27.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And becoming an adult is difficult work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I can forget for now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:33.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The night is waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:38.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As our hearts beat excitedly in rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:41.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And we frolic about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:44.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I nearly realize
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:48.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The feelings I want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:51.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if we are afraid of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You cannot move if you remain empty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:02:02.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all right if we have fun, so let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:05.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I forget all my troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:08.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and dance the night away with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:15.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll become someone more wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This endless Golden Time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:22.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The distance between us as you approach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Neither closes nor widens
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:29.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll treasure this even it it's the long way around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah! Kaga-san, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:51.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, Kaga-san and I are leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, you don't look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? Kaga-san's sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:08.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She wanted me to tell you she didn't think she could make it to class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:13.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I've got class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:17.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.37,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(199,72)}No subject
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.37,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(165,217)}How's your cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.06,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(384,282)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sending
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.06,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(380,318)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Message
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:32.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}In our discussion of natural law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:32.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san didn't come to class for a while after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}we cannot ignore the existence of an Englishman named Jeremy Bentham...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:33.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,According to her texts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(99,354)}her condition worsened, and she felt terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.41,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(333,51)}{\i1}How's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.41,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(331,90)}{\i1}your cold?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.21,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(347,173)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Sending{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.21,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(333,209)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Message{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't get to see Kaga-san over the weekend, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then, on Monday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good morning, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:59.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't go meet you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:06.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You still look a little sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stay home forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We have practice with the festival club today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, you really shouldn't force yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, you should get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You seem to be getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We heard you're dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I saw you holding hands and walking together the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:37.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you were just friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:38.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wasn't lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't bully the cute little underclassman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:52.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:52.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Our outfits are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,These are for the dudes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and those are for the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Try them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Those are loaners, so make sure you don't lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Take good care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It might be a little tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Lose some weight before the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where did Kaga-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It looks so good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:29.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We look pretty nice in these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko-chan, you look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, you look great in Japanese clothes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:46.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, there's something wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe you're still sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, do you need a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I haven't used this today, so it's still clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you really love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Will you love me forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When will you leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you find it annoying that I'm asking you this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:29.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you still love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:40.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did I do something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:44.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:49.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I keep thinking negative thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:00.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to be cute for you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:05.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No matter what I do, I feel anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:14.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't need to feel anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:29.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In the summer of my third year of high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I comforted Linda in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The current Banri doesn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Only I, a ghost, and Linda know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,U boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.49,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(53,44)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Note: Croatian for "to battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,U boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's time to start running!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's burn as hot as the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,U boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,U boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda has an older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He coached our high school's soccer team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda and I both called him Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:12.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, you guys are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:19.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey! Working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You seem to be working hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:23.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:28.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm trying to train them as hard as I can over summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:32.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We've finished practice, so we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:33.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:38.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll introduce my fiancée to you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay. Can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's kind and good at cooking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:48.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I still can't believe I'm marrying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I hope I can meet her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:52.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,U boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,U boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:02.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He works so hard at coaching, even though he doesn't get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's even using his own summer vacation to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need to talk to you about something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:15.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,An affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:23.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I saw my brother's fiancée leaving another man's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It must've been something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A friend, or maybe a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They kissed when she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I haven't told my brother yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think he'd believe me if I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He seems to really love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:49.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to get photographic evidence and destroy their marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:50.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:55.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Unless I send the pictures to everyone in both families and completely ruin her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't be satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:02.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll make her pay so much in reparations, she won't be able to make a living!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:06.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want her to live a miserable life, branded a cheater,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:09.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so she'll be lonely until the day she dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:11.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Am I wrong, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:20.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Am I trying to do something I shouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:26.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm really angry right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm thinking straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:33.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why I want your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you think, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:38.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:43.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't want your brother to marry a woman like her, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's your brother's fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:32.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought we were going to catch her in the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If we enter the apartment now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,we should be able to get even more damning pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I told you, just wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:22.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't sit back and watch a nice guy like your brother be betrayed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but let's try to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:38.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you get a picture of them linking arms on your phone, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:44.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I did, but we need something more decisive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Would you erase it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.33,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(299,211)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Erase all
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.33,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(300,242)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.33,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(307,272)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}YES/NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.03,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(294,217)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}All pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.03,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(298,244)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}have been
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.03,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(314,273)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}erased
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:56.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:56.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll wear the mask of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:04.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nana-chan, what a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk with you inside your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:28.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:14.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you still want to get married,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:17.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,please don't do this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll forget about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't drive until you've calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Be careful you don't get in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:45.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's been watching us the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I told her not to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I understand."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:13.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:14.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's better than destroying everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:25.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As long as I pretend like I don't know anything, things will work out as they always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It'll be like nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is that really the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:36.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want to hurt my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of making him sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's for your brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:48.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you really think pretending nothing happened is what's best for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It'll last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's going to be family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can you think of her as your own sister-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Imagine how your parents would feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:04.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everything you said is exactly right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:09.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I may have been wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've already done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:18.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Besides, you don't need to be so harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've really done it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:30.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can endure this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My brother's going to live a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And I'm one of the liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I did the wrong thing, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I saw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you don't have to suffer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:13.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I may be unreliable, and I may not be able to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...but I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll always be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:45.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When you want to scream or cry, I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll share your feelings and stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if you think I'm a nuisance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,no matter where you go, I'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:55.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll always be listening for your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When the rain falls, when the wind blows...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:12.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...when the flowers scatter, when shadows loom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:18.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In every sign, I'll search for your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I promise I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can I really trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:39.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't have the confidence to answer her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But because of this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:46.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,my feelings for Linda became so strong,\NI couldn't hold them back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:51.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The seasons changed, and winter came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was forced to clearly recognize my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda... Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:07.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where's Kouko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Her cold came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's not coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:15.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She didn't seem to have much energy yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She rested all weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:21.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She was acting weird yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:30.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, you were sad because you couldn't spend the weekend with your beloved Kouko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What about you, Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What did you do this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, to Shizuoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:44.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't go home for Golden Week,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and my parents told me to come home now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm kind of tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's nothing serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I saw my big brother again, among other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, you have an older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I need to get to my next class!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, make sure you take good care of Kouko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Always listen for Kouko-chan's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When the rain falls, when the wind blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When the flowers scatter, when shadows loom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:30.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In every sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:33.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...search for her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:35.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:39.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko-chan is your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:40.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:52.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I had looked her in the eye and answered her then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:56.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,would things have turned out differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Would I have not become a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:01.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Would I still be by Linda's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can I really trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I should have told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:12.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I love you, Linda."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"That's why I want you to trust me."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:17.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I should have told her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's too late for regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:24.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda and I are hopelessly far apart now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:28.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have a body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:52.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:55.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:19.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In one hand in the sweetened cafe latte I love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:23.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The moment I smiled I could smell love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:28.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to wear my cherry-colored dress perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:33.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My heart beats quietly as I rush to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:35.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,(Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:37.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watch out for that sweet trap
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:39.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,(Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:41.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll whisper to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:44.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}(Hey, I'm a little anxious)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:46.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, I long for this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:50.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How should I smile when I see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:53.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Pretty love, pretty love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:55.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Under the sky, under sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:00.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's hold hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:05.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't be honest about my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:10.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But pull me along by my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:40.78,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(55,406)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}In The Mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:28.20,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(326,361)}U boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:29.60,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(237,361)}Working hard, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:30.94,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(244,360)}What? Is that, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:31.91,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(253,358)}...the Eiffel Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.21,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(208,358)}What? It's the Awa dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:34.81,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(339,358)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.11,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(229,361)}Yes, I'm working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:36.94,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(261,361)}I'm Awa dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:38.41,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(128,361)}What did you mean by the Eiffel Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:40.78,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(151,361)}Well, that's, er, it's... I can't tell you.
